<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">Portwood <span>DocGen</span></div>
        <nav class="header-links">
            <a href="/DocGenGuide">User Guide</a>
            <a href="/DocGenRoadmap">Roadmap</a>
            <a href="/DocGenCommunity">Community</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Portwood-Global-Solutions/Portwood-DocGen">GitHub</a>
            <a href="/DocGenSupport" style="color: #fbbf24;">Support the Project</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openInstallModal()" style="color: #60a5fa;">Install</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge-row">
            <span class="badge green">100% Free Forever</span>
            <span class="badge">100% Native Salesforce</span>
            <span class="badge">Your Data Never Leaves Your Org</span>
            <span class="badge green">Open Source</span>
            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!installCount > 0}">
                <span class="badge green">Proudly serving {!installCount} org{!IF(installCount > 1, 's', '')}</span>
            </apex:outputPanel>
        </div>
        <h1>Document Generation<br/>for <span>Salesforce</span></h1>
        <p>Generate polished PDFs and Word documents from any Salesforce record. Pull in related records, images, barcodes, totals, and more — all from a simple Word template.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openInstallModal()" class="btn btn-primary">Install Free</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openInstallModal()" class="btn btn-secondary">Install in Sandbox</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-map">
            <p class="hero-map-label" id="map-subtitle">Reducing document generation costs worldwide</p>
            <div id="docgen-map"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="features">
        <h2>Everything you need. Nothing you don't.</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128196;</div>
                <h3>PDF &amp; Word Output</h3>
                <p>Generate professional PDFs and Word documents from your own branded Word templates. Just add placeholder tags and upload.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128257;</div>
                <h3>Point-and-Click Setup</h3>
                <p>Visual query builder lets you pick fields and related records without writing any code. Works with any standard or custom object.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128248;</div>
                <h3>Images &amp; Barcodes</h3>
                <p>Embed logos, photos, and images from your Salesforce records. Add Code 128 barcodes and QR codes to PDFs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#9889;</div>
                <h3>Automate with Flows</h3>
                <p>Trigger document generation from Salesforce Flows — auto-generate invoices, contracts, or reports when records change. Sample Flows included.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128218;</div>
                <h3>Bulk Generation</h3>
                <p>Generate documents for hundreds of records at once from list views or reports. Perfect for batch invoicing, statements, and mail merges.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128274;</div>
                <h3>Secure &amp; Reliable</h3>
                <p>100% native — your data never leaves Salesforce. Respects all sharing rules and field-level security. Tested at scale with 10,000+ row documents.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

